prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A whimsical and humorous fantasy scene combining snowboarding and sushi. In the center, Jordan from the photo, transformed into a cartoon character, is skillfully snowboarding down a giant, glistening California roll as if it were a snowy half-pipe. He wears a gray jacket over a maroon t-shirt (logos omitted) and has a joyful, concentrated expression. His snowboard kicks up a spray of rice and tobiko instead of snow. Lao Lao, also as a cartoon character based on the photo, wears her glasses and a light-colored jacket, gleefully riding on Jordan's shoulders. She's laughing and holding a pair of oversized chopsticks, trying to catch flying pieces of shrimp tempura and avocado that are tossed up by their movement.

The background is a dreamy, magical mountain range made entirely of sushi. The peaks are topped with dollops of wasabi and pickled ginger, and the landscape is dotted with nigiri "trees" and sashimi "rivers" under a soft, pastel-colored sky with fluffy, cloud-like formations of soy sauce. The overall aesthetic is ethereal and fantastical, with a lighthearted and funny tone.

In the upper-middle area, the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The composition is dynamic and full of playful energy.
